{"title_page": "List of gravity hills", "text_new": "This is a '''list of gravity hills and magnetic hills''' around the world.\n\nA [[gravity hill]] is a place where a slight downhill slope appears to be an uphill slope due to the layout of the surrounding land, creating the [[optical illusion]] that water flows uphill or that a car left out of gear will roll uphill. Many of these sites have no specific name and are often called just \"Gravity Hill\", \"Magnetic Hill\", \"Magic Road\" or something similar.\n<!--PLEASE DON'T ADD ANY UNLESS YOU INCLUDE A REFERENCE-->\n{{TOC right}}\n\n==Australia==\n<!--PLEASE DON'T ADD ANY UNLESS YOU INCLUDE A REFERENCE-->\n[[File:Orroroo, Magnetic Hill.JPG|thumb|right|Magnetic Hill in [[Orroroo, South Australia]]]]\n\n*[[Bowen Mountain, New South Wales]]: Bowen Mountain Road, shortly after turnoff from Grose Vale Road. Known as Magnetic Mountain. Hill starts at intersection of Bowen Mountain Road and Westbury Road<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eureka4you.com/magnetichillworldwide/Richmond-NSW.htm |title=Magnetic Hill - Richmond, NSW |publisher=Eureka4you.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n*[[Moonbi, New South Wales]], near [[Tamworth, New South Wales|Tamworth]]: \"Gravity Hill\" near the Moonbi lookout<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eureka4you.com/magnetichillworldwide/Moonbi-NSW.htm |title=Magnetic Hill - Moonbi, NSW. Australia |publisher=Eureka4you.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n*[[Orroroo, South Australia]]: Magnetic Hill<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eureka4you.com/magnetichillworldwide/Peterborough-SA.htm |title=Magnetic Hill - Peterborough - South Australia |publisher=Eureka4you.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref><ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/radio/adelaide/programs/afternoons/magnetic-hill/8583982 Magnetic Hill - magnetic forces pulling cars or optical illusion?], [[ABC Adelaide]], 2 June 2017</ref>\n*[[Woodend, Victoria|Woodend]], [[Hanging Rock, Victoria]]: Straws Lane<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.news.com.au/travel/australia/hanging-for-a-perfect-picnic-spot/story-e6frfq90-1111113167023 |title=Hanging for a perfect picnic spot |publisher=news.com.au |date= |accessdate=2012-08-18}}</ref>\n\n==Brazil==\n[[File:Rua amendoim placa.JPG|thumb|right|Sign for ''Rua do Amendoim'', in [[Belo Horizonte]], Brazil]]\n\n*[[Belo Horizonte]], [[Minas Gerais]]: Rua Professor Ot\u00e1vio Coelho de Magalh\u00e3es (official name), popularly known as ''Rua do Amendoim'' ([[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] for \"Peanut Street\")<ref>{{cite web |url=http://super.abril.com.br/cultura/a-rua-do-sobe-desce |title=A rua do sobe-desce |language=PT |trans-title=The up and down street |publisher=Editora Abril (Superinteressante) |date=April 1999 |accessdate=2016-05-13}}</ref><ref>http://www.projetoockham.org/ferramentas_metodo_5.html</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://worldofsupernatural.blogspot.com/2008/08/mystery-of-ladeira-do-amendoim-slope-of.html |title=The world of the supernatural: The mystery of \"Ladeira do Amendoim\" (Slope of the Peanut) |publisher=Worldofsupernatural.blogspot.com |date=2008-08-19 |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref> \n*[[Exu, Pernambuco|Exu]], [[Pernambuco]]: [[BR-122]], public road connecting Exu to [[Bodoc\u00f3]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.flatout.com.br/nesta-ladeira-em-pernambuco-os-carros-descem-para-cima/ |title=In this Pernambuco's Road, cars descend upwards |publisher=Flatout |date=2014-04-15 |accessdate=2014-04-15}}</ref>\n\n==Canada==\n<!--PLEASE DON'T ADD ANY UNLESS YOU INCLUDE A REFERENCE-->\n[[File:Magnetic Hill Quebec 09.jpg|thumb|right|Magnetic Hill in [[Chartierville, Quebec]]]]\n\n*[[Abbotsford, British Columbia]]: McKee Road just before Ledgeview Golf Course<ref>{{cite web|url=http://userpages.umbc.edu/~frizzell/gravhills.html |title=Gravity Hills |publisher=Userpages.umbc.edu |date= |accessdate=2013-10-09}}</ref>\n*[[Vernon, British Columbia]]: 5390 Dixon Dam Road<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sharphooks.com/search.aspx?subpage=hotelinfo&hotelid=7238 |title=Magnetic Hill B&B}}</ref>\n*[[Moncton, New Brunswick]]: [[Magnetic Hill (Moncton)|Magnetic Hill]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.magnetichill.com/english.htm |title=Magnetic Hill |publisher=Magnetic Hill |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903143424/http://www.magnetichill.com/english.htm |archivedate=2011-09-03 |df= }}</ref>\n*[[Bridgetown, Nova Scotia]]: on Hampton Mountain Road {{convert|2|km|1|abbr=on}} south of Valleyview Provincial Park<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.checkinnovascotia.com/Public/main/event.asp?key=ATT004 |title=Magnetic Hill - Bridgetown |author= |website=Check In Nova Scotia. - Nova Scotia Tourism Information Pages |publisher=Nova Scotia, Dept. of Tourism, Culture & Heritage. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110210433/http://www.checkinnovascotia.com/Public/main/event.asp?key=ATT004 |archivedate=2008-01-10 |url-status=dead |df= }}</ref>\n*[[Burlington, Ontario]]: King Road, just north of Bayview Park. Stop car at \"No Motorized Vehicles\" sign, face south.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eureka4you.com/magnetichill/index.htm |title=Magnetic Hill - Burlington - Ontario |publisher=Eureka4you.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n*[[Caledon, Ontario]]: Escarpment Sideroad approaching Highway 10, stop car at tunnel<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldfortravel.com/2015/01/17/illusionary-magnetic-hills-canada/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513184009/http://www.worldfortravel.com/2015/01/17/illusionary-magnetic-hills-canada/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=2016-05-13 |title=Illusionary Magnetic Hills \u2013 Canada |accessdate=2016-12-28 }}</ref>\n*[[Dacre, Ontario]]: Highway 41, near intersection with Highway 132, known as Magnetic Hill<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eureka4you.com/magnetichillworldwide/Dacre-ON.htm |title=Magnetic Hill - Dacre, Ontario |publisher=Eureka4you.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n*[[Oshawa, Ontario]]: Ritson Road N (north of Raglan Road); just south of tracks, start near large tree on left, you should roll towards tracks.<ref name=\"Eureka4you.com\">{{cite web |url=http://www.provincequebec.com/forests-parc-mountains-quebec/magnetic-hill/ |title=Magnetic Hill - Chartierville, Quebec |publisher=Provincequebec.com |date= |accessdate=2016-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913225806/http://www.provincequebec.com/forests-parc-mountains-quebec/magnetic-hill/ |archive-date=2016-09-13 |url-status=dead |df= }}</ref>\n*[[Chartierville, Quebec]]: Magnetic Hill<ref name=\"Eureka4you.com\"/>\n*[[Notre-Dame-Auxiliatrice-de-Buckland, Quebec]]: Route Saint-Louis (C\u00f4te magn\u00e9tique de Buckland)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.buckland.qc.ca/indexFr.asp?numero=91 |title=Attraits |publisher=Municipalit\u00e9 de Notre-Dame-Auxiliatrice-de-Buckland |date= |accessdate=2013-10-26}}</ref>\n\n==China==\n*[[Gansu]]: a {{convert|200|ft|0|abbr=on|disp=flip}} slope at an angle of 15&nbsp;degrees in a desert region of [[Sunan Yugur Autonomous County|Sunan County]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.science-frontiers.com/sf125/sf125p10.htm |title=Two Non-falls |publisher=Science-frontiers.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n\n==Cyprus==\n*[[Paphos]]: Just after Droushia exit to [[Polis, Cyprus|Polis]] main road. Coordinates: 34.982930 32.405960.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.paphostravelguide.com/AntiGravity-Road---Optical-Illusion-in-Paphos.php|date=2013-07-05|title=AntiGravity Road - Optical Illusion in Paphos|accessdate=2013-07-07|language=cs|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121161750/https://www.paphostravelguide.com/AntiGravity-Road---Optical-Illusion-in-Paphos.php|archive-date=2018-11-21|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n==Czech Republic==\n*Ka\u010derov near [[Zdobnice]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.toulkypocechach.com/anomalie.php |title=Gravita\u010dn\u00ed anom\u00e1lie u Ka\u010derova |access-date=2016-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102150812/http://www.toulkypocechach.com/anomalie.php |archive-date=2016-11-02 |url-status=dead |df= }}</ref>\n*[[Moravsk\u00e1 T\u0159ebov\u00e1]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ba4BpZHyzhg |title=Gravity Hill - Moravsk\u00e1 T\u0159ebov\u00e1 |publisher=Youtube.com |date=2008-08-05 |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n\n==Dominican Republic==\n*[[Polo, Dominican Republic|Polo]]: El Polo Magn\u00e9tico (\"The Magnetic Pole\")<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eureka4you.com/magnetichillworldwide/Cabral-DR.htm |title=Magnetic Pole - Cabral, Barahona. Dominican Republic |publisher=Eureka4you.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref>\n\n==India==\n*On the Mainpat [[Ulta Pani]] and {{ill|Chhatre}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://beautyofchhattisgarh.blogspot.com/2020/04/ShimlaofChhattisgarhMainpat.html |title=Shimla of Chhattisgarh |publisher=beautyofchhattisgarh.blogspot.com }}{{date=April 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\n==Greece==\n*At the road to [[Leivithra]], [[Pieria (regional unit)|Pieria]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pieria.tv/\u03bc\u03b1\u03b3\u03bd\u03b7\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03bf-\u03c0\u03b5\u03b4\u03b9\u03bf-\u03bb\u03b5\u03b9\u03b2\u03b7\u03b8\u03c1\u03b1-\u03b1\u03bd\u03b1\u03c4\u03bf\u03bb\u03b9\u03ba\u03bf\u03c5|title=\u039c\u03b1\u03b3\u03bd\u03b7\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03bf \u03c0\u03b5\u03b4\u03b9\u03bf \u039b\u03b5\u03b9\u03b2\u03ae\u03b8\u03c1\u03c9\u03bd|last=|first=|date=|website=pieria.tv|publisher=pieria.tv|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n==Guatemala==\n*Paso Misterioso, on the road from Cocales, [[Suchitep\u00e9quez Department|Suchitep\u00e9quez]] to [[San Lucas Tolim\u00e1n]], [[Solol\u00e1]], about {{convert|130|km|0|abbr=on}} from the [[Guatemala City|capital city]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.viajeros.com/diarios/guatemala/subida-o-bajada |title=Subida o Bajada? |publisher=Viajeros.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.clubbyb.com/index.php?id=125 |title=Sabias Que?... El paso 