.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.clubbyb.com/index.php?id=125 |title=Sabias Que?... El paso misterioso |publisher=Clubbyb.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-03 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708165419/http://www.clubbyb.com/index.php?id=125 |archivedate=2011-07-08 |df= }}</ref>\n\n==India==\n{{see also | Krishna's Butterball }}\n[[File:Magnetic Hill (India) sign.jpg|thumb|A [[Border Roads Organisation]] [[Himank]] sign near the [[Magnetic Hill (India)|Magnetic Hill]] in [[Ladakh]], India]]\n\n* [[Chhattisgarh]] state: \n** [[Surguja district]] - [[Mainpat#Gravity_Hill|Ulta Pani magnetic hill]]: also called ''Bisar paani magnetic hill'', is located at [[Mainpat]] hill station<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.patrika.com/ambikapur-news/you-will-shocked-in-cgs-shimla-heres-stream-flows-reverse-see-video-1-2165976/|title=Chhattisgarh facts: \u091b\u0924\u094d\u0924\u0940\u0938\u0917\u0922\u093c \u0915\u093e \u0936\u093f\u092e\u0932\u093e \u0915\u0930 \u0926\u0947\u0917\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0930\u093e\u0928, \u092f\u0939\u093e\u0902 \u091a\u0922\u093c\u093e\u0908 \u0915\u0940 \u0913\u0930 \u092c\u0939\u0924\u0940 \u0939\u0948 \u0927\u093e\u0930\u093e, \u0928\u093e\u092e \u0939\u0948 \u0909\u0932\u094d\u091f\u093e\u092a\u093e\u0928\u0940- \u0926\u0947\u0916\u0947\u0902 Video|website=www.patrika.com}}</ref><ref>http://abc.action.news/watch?v=DWbeywjx13A</ref> 70 km south of [[Ambikapur, India|Ambikapur]] city.\n** [[Kabirdham district]] - [[Pandariya#Gravity_hill_optical_illusion|Dewanpatpar magnetic hill]]: is 40 km north of [[Pandariya]] on State Highway SH5 in Kabirdham district (formerly Kawardha district).<ref name=DP1>{{cite web|url=https://getlink.pro/v/TwkPO8EFfXQ|title=Dewanpatpar magnetic hill, Kudrat ka KARISHMA - The Magnetic Hill where Rules of Gravity ends}}</ref>\n\n* [[Gujarat]] state:\n**  [[Amreli district]] - [[Tulsishyam#Gravity_hill_optical_illusion|Tulsishyam Anti Gravity Hill]]:<ref nam