nicze.25/Niewiarygodna,gora,Zar.752.html |title=MasterMinds: Niewiarygodna gora Zar |access-date=2014-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006100844/http://www.masterminds.pl/Tajemnicze.25/Niewiarygodna,gora,Zar.752.html |archive-date=2014-10-06 |url-status=dead |df= }}</ref> there is a road segment ca. {{convert|200|m|ft|abbr=in}} long circling the mountain where \"cars roll uphill\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7-5n97ZPJhc |title=YouTube: Niesamowite miejsca - G\u00f3ra \u017bar}}</ref>\n* The ''Czarodziejska G\u00f3rka'' is a 200-meter stretch of the road between [[Str\u0105czno]] and [[Rutwica]] near [[Wa\u0142cz]] in north-west Poland where objects, including cars, roll uphill.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.polskaniezwykla.pl/web/place/17651,rutwica-magnetyczna-gorka.html |title=Magnetyczna g\u00f3rka}}</ref>\n\n==Portugal==\n*[[Braga]]: the road behind [[Bom Jesus do Monte]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tsf.pt/blogs/fimdarua/archive/2009/05/04/o-mist-233-rio-da-estrada-do-bom-jesus.aspx |title=O mist\u00e9rio da estrada do Bom Jesus - Blogue TSF - Fim da Rua - Blogue TSF |publisher=Tsf.pt |date=1999-02-22 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227202817/http://www.tsf.pt/blogs/fimdarua/archive/2009/05/04/o-mist-233-rio-da-estrada-do-bom-jesus.aspx |archivedate=2013-12-27 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Tempo para criar p\u00e1gina:&nbsp;1.84&nbsp;segundos |url=http://www.zeitgeistportugal.org/capitulo/index.php?option=com_kunena&func=view&catid=14&id=12584&Itemid=56 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130416062329/http://www.zeitgeistportugal.org/capitulo/index.php?option=com_kunena&func=view&catid=14&id=12584&Itemid=56 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2013-04-16 |title=Descidas que se \"sobe\" e Subidas que se \"desce\" por gravidade |publisher=Zeitgeistportugal.org |date= |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tsf.pt/PaginaInicial/Vida/Interior.a